    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Using tags can help you organize your customer profile list. You can use tags to
                label your customers with categories or descriptive terms. For example, if you have
                wholesale customers, then you can tag those customers as wholesale.</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
